tugboat at about 7:00 a.m. local time on Sunday. Four people died
on the spot and 30 went missing.
</P>
<P>
Smog that has reduced visibility to 3-5 meters was blamed for
the accident.
</P>
<P>
The skippers of the ship and the tugboat are under police
custody for questioning, as efforts to rescue the victims are
continuing, the reports said.  
