<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 22 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today dropped 7 HK dollars to close at 2,985 HK dollars a tael,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 323.33 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, down 0.78 U.S. dollar from the previous close at today's
exchange rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7495 HK dollars. 
</P>
