<HEADLINE> Norwegian King Arrives in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 22 (Xinhua) -- Norwegian King Harald V arrived
here this evening by plane for a state visit to China, at the
invitation of Chinese President Jiang Zemin.
</P>
<P>
This is the first visit to China by Harald V after his
enthronement in 1991.
</P>
<P>
The Norwegian King's entourage includes Queen Sonja, foreign
minister Knut Vollebaek, businessmen and journalists.
</P>
<P>
Among those greeting the Norwegian visitors at the airport were
Chairman of the Chinese Government Reception Committee and
Vice-Minister of Water Resources Zhang Chunyuan, Chinese
Ambassador to Norway Zhu Yinglu, and Vice-Foreign Minister Wang
Yingfan.  
</P>
