<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, October 21 (Xinhua) -- A Danish nurse working in a
Copenhagen hospital has been detained on the charge of killing 22
elderly patients.
</P>
<P>
The Danish News Agency reported today that the 32-year-old
nurse killed the old people by injecting them with a
morphine-based drug.
</P>
