<HEADLINE> China to Control Production of PC </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 22 (Xinhua) -- China's personal computer
market is expected to witness annual sales of ten million PCs in
2000, ranking second or third in the world, reported today's China
Daily.
</P>
<P>
