<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, October 21 (Xinhua) -- Brazilian striker Bebeto could
face legal action as his club Deportivo Coruna claimed that Bebeto
had failed to fulfil his contract.
</P>
<P>
Bebeto was unable to return to Spain on Monday, the deadline he
had consulted with the club. And a spokeman at the club said on
