<HEADLINE> Cuban Party Holds Meeting on Socialism in Next Century </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, October 21 (Xinhua) -- The Cuban Communist Party held a
meeting called "Socialism for the 21st Century" here today to
discuss the socialism as an alternative to the open market.
</P>
<P>
The gathering will also discuss the reality of contemporary
socialism, the vogue of Marxism and Leninism in the actual world
and the imperialism at the end of the century.
</P>
