Sources said Tung assured Blair that things had gone well in
Hong Kong since it was returned to China on July 1 after 156 years
of British colonial rule.
</P>
<P>
Tung arrived here this morning for a three-day visit to
Britain. His trip is aimed at strengthening the close economic and
trade ties between Hong Kong and Britain. 
